# Merchant Refund Portal

A full-stack production-grade refund management system where merchants can view transactions and initiate refunds while enforcing strict eligibility rules.

---

# Live Application

Frontend
https://merchant-refund-portal-lime.vercel.app/

Backend API
https://merchant-refund-portal.onrender.com

